summary: An Ordinance authorizing, empowering and directing the Corporation Counsel to dismiss cause No. 67256, records of the Superior Court of King County, Washington, being a proceeding for the condemnation of certain lots in Thomas Gem Tract, as provided in Ordinance No. 2268, in so far as the same affects Lots Nine (9) and Ten (10), in Block Four (4), Thomas Gem Tract, directing the cancellation of the lis pendens as to said Lots 9 and 10, and declaring an emergency.
